OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782038883
OL,3,CMajor motorway closed as thousands
OL,4,Ctake part in tribute to Hairy Biker
OL,6,FA carriageway of a busy motorway was
OL,7,Fclosed to traffic to allow thousands
OL,8,Fof motorcyclists to pay their final
OL,9,Ftribute to one of the Hairy Bikers.
OL,11,FOfficers temporarily stopped vehicles
OL,12,Fon the M6 in Cheshire on Saturday to
OL,13,Fallow riders to set off on the last
OL,14,Flegs of their final journey for Dave
OL,15,FDay.
OL,17,FDave Myers from Barrow-in-Furness,
OL,18,FCumbria, died in February 2024, two
OL,19,Fyears after he revealed he had been
OL,20,Fdiagnosed with cancer.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
