OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782038883
OL,3,CMajor motorway closed as thousands
OL,4,Ctake part in tribute to Hairy Biker
OL,6,FThe much-loved TV presenter, who was
OL,7,Fhalf of the Hairy Bikers duo along
OL,8,Fwith Si King, inspired the 300-mile
OL,9,Fjourney for charity.
OL,11,FDubbed 'The Last Ride Home',
OL,12,Forganisers said the aim of the day was
OL,13,F"to spread hope and happiness to all
OL,14,Fregardless of who you are or where
OL,15,Fyou're from, honouring and remembering
OL,16,FDave and all other lost loved ones."
OL,18,FThe route began in London, via breaks
OL,19,Fat Oxford, Solihull, Knutsford and
OL,20,FLancaster.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
