CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782038883
OL,3,CMajor motorway closed as thousands
OL,4,Ctake part in tribute to Hairy Biker
OL,6,FBosses for the M6 Toll in Birmingham
OL,7,Fagreed free passage for all motorbikes
OL,8,Ftaking part.
OL,10,FFrom makeup artist to TV chef - who
OL,11,Fwas 'Hairy Biker' Dave Myers? >
OL,13,FParticipants also joined from
OL,14,FScotland, the North, and the East
OL,15,Fbefore meeting at the finish line
OL,16,Foutside Barrow-in-Furness Town Hall on
OL,17,FDuke Street.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
