CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782038883
OL,3,CMajor motorway closed as thousands
OL,4,Ctake part in tribute to Hairy Biker
OL,6,FThe ride saw scores of people taking
OL,7,Fto motorway bridges up and down
OL,8,FEngland to catch a glimpse of the
OL,9,Fspectacle.
OL,11,FEarlier this year, organiser Jason
OL,12,FWoodcock confirmed the fundraiser
OL,13,Fwould be the last of its kind because
OL,14,Fof financial challenges.
OL,16,FDave's close friend explained the
OL,17,Fevent would go "back to basics" after
OL,18,Fbeing asked to take on "impossible"
OL,19,Fcosts of up to #100,000.
