OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782038883
OL,3,CMajor motorway closed as thousands
OL,4,Ctake part in tribute to Hairy Biker
OL,6,FOrganisers estimate up to over 75,000
OL,7,Fbikes took part in two previous
OL,8,Fevents, raising over #250,000.
OL,10,FThis year's ride has already raised
OL,11,Fmore than #31,000 for Childline and
OL,12,Flocal good causes in Barrow-in-Furness.
OL,14,FDonations can be made here.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
